        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR2a0007-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:14:26.652+09:00">这时，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:14:50.215+09:00">东平国王因为自己是皇上至亲而骄横奢侈，不遵法令，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:15:03.004+09:00">前任太傅和国相因东平王而连连获罪。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:15:10.491+09:00">到王尊上任理事，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:15:40.189+09:00">他捧着皇帝的任命文书来到宫中，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:15:46.181+09:00">东平王没及时出来接受文书，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:15:52.466+09:00">王尊便拿着文书回住处，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:15:58.304+09:00">吃罢饭才返回王宫。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:16:08.117+09:00">将诏书送上后，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:16:12.546+09:00">便拜见东平王，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:16:19.479+09:00">太傅在王尊面前说起《相鼠》那首诗。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:16:22.737+09:00">王尊说：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:16:35.574+09:00">“别拿着布鼓过雷门，卖弄本领！“</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:16:43.288+09:00">东平王发怒，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:16:45.486+09:00">起身进入后宫。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:17:01.486+09:00">王尊也返身出宫，径直跑回住所。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:17:24.215+09:00">先前，东平王多次私自外出，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:17:28.181+09:00">骑着马在国中驱逐奔弛，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:17:52.376+09:00">与后姬的家族相勾结。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:17:58.417+09:00">王尊到任后，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:18:00.984+09:00">召来掌管车马的既长，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:18:05.264+09:00">告诫他：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:18:20.952+09:00">“大王外出应当有官属相随，配上鸣铃仪仗才可出发，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.25" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:18:37.242+09:00">从现在起若有人命你驾小车私自外出，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.26" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:18:40.77+09:00">要磕头规劝，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.27" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:18:48.798+09:00">就说国相教的不能这样做。”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.28" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:18:53.108+09:00">后来王尊朝见东平王，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.29" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:18:54.189+09:00">东平王又请他登上大堂。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.30" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:19:32.537+09:00">王尊对东平王说：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.31" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:19:40.209+09:00">“王尊来作大王的国相时，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.32" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:19:45.06+09:00">人们都为我忧伤，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.33" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:19:53.826+09:00">因王尊不能为朝廷所容，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.34" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:21:06.846+09:00">故而被派来辅助大王。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.35" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:21:13.814+09:00">天下人都说大王勇敢，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.36" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:21:17.436+09:00">我想只是依仗富贵的话，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.37" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:21:21.208+09:00">又怎么谈得上勇敢？</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.38" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:21:25.114+09:00">像我王尊才算得上勇敢哩。“</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.39" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:22:24.047+09:00">东平王脸色一变，盯着王尊，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.40" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:22:28.991+09:00">想要刺杀他，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.41" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:22:35.017+09:00">便假装友好的样子对王尊说：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.42" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:22:43.461+09:00">“我想看看国相的佩刀是什么模样。”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.43" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:22:46.755+09:00">王尊抬起双臂，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.44" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:22:50.718+09:00">回头对旁边的侍郎说：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.45" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:23:22.328+09:00">“请你向前替我抽出佩刀来给大王看，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.46" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:23:25.894+09:00">不然，大王就会诬陷我，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.47" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:24:49.467+09:00">东平王见自己的企图被识破了，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.48" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:24:53.927+09:00">又素闻王尊大名，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.49" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:25:01.607+09:00">深为王尊所折服，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.50" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:25:06.404+09:00">设酒备宴，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.51" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:25:39.324+09:00">与王尊对饮，极为欢快。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.52" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:26:16.1+09:00">太后征史上书弹劾王尊：“做国相傲慢不忠，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.53" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:26:22.232+09:00">而东平王血气未定，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.54" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:26:25.177+09:00">难以忍受。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.55" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:26:50.085+09:00">我实在担心我们母子难免同死。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.56" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:27:03.133+09:00">从今后我不愿再叫东平王见到王尊。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.57" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:27:10.576+09:00">皇上要是不答应，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.58" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:27:16.988+09:00">我愿首先自杀，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.59" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:27:24.912+09:00">我不忍心看着东平王失去做国王的尊严。”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.60" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:27:28.181+09:00">王尊竟因此被削职为民。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.61" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:27:53.243+09:00">大将军王凤上奏请求让王尊补缺做了军中司马，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-46a.62" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-02-09T03:28:27.714+09:00">后来提升为司隶校尉。</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
